8 DAYS OF DOUGHNUTS 3/8 ✨🍩🎀 nutella doughnuts! 

ingredients:
one cup warm water (NOT HOT!!) 
1 pack active dry yeast (2.5 tablespoons)
3 cups flour -add them slowly not at once & add a bit more if too sticky
3 tablespoons sugar 
1/2 stick of unsalted butter 
1 big tablespoon of nutella (could add more too if you like a lot) 

let me know he dough rise for about an hour - 2 hours and shape as you like. let rest a bit more (15-30 minutes) and fry with canola oil. enjoy!!! ❤️
